Description:

Jenna Jameson received an AVN Award for playing a disturbed young woman with revenge on her mind, stalking radio talk-show therapist (Tiffany Million) whom she blames for the breakup of her relationship. Intense action and sex make this one a hit. Directed by Brad Armstrong and Greg Steel.


What happens when you mess with our girl Jenna? It seems that a certain Dr. Cypress, famed radio talk-show host, is about to find out. That little bitch has done her wrong, and Jenna's pissed! Something tells us the good Doctor's in for a little surprise. So sit back with The Wicked One and savor the sweet taste of revenge
